<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Novellus cut on price.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Novellus cut on price.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Lehman Brothers said analyst Edward White downgraded Novellus Systems inc Inc to outperform from buy based on the recent sharp price appreciation in the shares.</p>
<p>-- In a note, Lehman said it still thinks Novellus shares offer upside potential, &quot;but at the current level we do not recommend purchasing them as urgently.&quot;</p>
<p>-- Also said Novellus' share valuation &quot;is not excessive, so this is not a veiled sell recommendation.&quot;</p>
<p>-- Shares rose 1-1/2 to 80.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1730))</p>
